Code Bubble Sort

Provided with a random integer array/list(ARR) of size N, you have been required to sort this array using 'Bubble Sort'.

Solution:

public class Solution {  

    public static void bubbleSort(int[] arr){
    	//Your code goes here
         int n=arr.length;
    for(int i=0;i<n-1;i++)
        {  
        for(int j=0;j<n-1-i;j++)
            {
                if(arr[j]>arr[j+1])
                {
                int temp=arr[j+1];
                 arr[j+1]=arr[j];
                 arr[j]=temp;
                }
            }
        }
    }  
}
